		<h1>What Does This App Do?</h1>
		<p>It pulls together a bunch of communications data to give you a picture of what actions you should take in your network.</p>
		<p>Whether you use LinkedIn, email, or your phone to get in touch with people, it's still the same person on the other side-- so this app synthesizes across those communications tools to give you a clear picture.</p>
		<h3>Current Features</h3>
		<ul>
			<li>Create tags for contacts for easier tracking</li>
			<li>See who you need to get back to, and when you last connected</li>
			<li>See who you are waiting on for a response, and how long you've been waiting</li>
		</ul>
